<div class="modules">
      <div class="module first">
            <h3><a href="#"  data-metrics='{"action":"Toggle Footer Dropdown","label":"About","category":"Planet Money"}' >About</a></h3>
      <div id="footer_module" class="agglocation linkLocation">
                  <div id="res163939331" class="bucketwrap listtext">
                        <div class="bucket">
                              <p>Imagine you could call up a friend and say, "Meet me at the bar and tell me what's going on with the economy." Now imagine that's actually a fun evening. That's what we're going for at <em>Planet Money</em>. Want to know more? <a href="https://www.npr.org/blogs/money/2011/04/27/135599807/about-planet-money">Check out our "about" page</a>. Want to connect with the <em>Planet Money</em> team? <a href="mailto:planetmoney@npr.org">Send us an email</a>.</p>
            </div>
            
